REQUIRE:
- Mailserver with IMAP-Support
- Roundcube Webmailclient (tested with roundcubemail-0.7)

INSTALL:
1. enable mail plugin
2. type your roundcubedir in the administrator-settings
3. optional type encryptionstrings (your mailuser and password will be crypted)
4. type your mail-username and mail-password in your personal settings
5. Aktivate your autologonplugin in Roundcube (you can find it in my zip file (rouncubeplugin)
7. Enjoy it or send me your bug to david@stuggis.de

Now we need a nice Theme for our OwnCloudRoundcube =D